                <Button x:Name="ClickSurface" HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="1280" Height="800" Opacity="0.01" />
                <TextBlock Name="tbDebugTextBlock" Visibility="Collapsed" Grid.Row="0" Margin="537,554,0,0" Foreground="Red" Background="White" Opacity="0.80" Height="200" Width="500" IsHitTestVisible="False">Debug Mode. <LineBreak />Hotspot Visualizations Enabled. <LineBreak />Press C to get to the next interaction. <LineBreak />Press M to move forward 10 seconds.<LineBreak />Press N to move backward 10 seconds.<LineBreak /> <LineBreak /> Debug Mode breaks some states in the game when you use it<LineBreak /> especially during interactions and bad-alternate endings.<LineBreak />Use it sparingly through an actual playthrough.</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Name="tbHelpText" Visibility="Collapsed" Grid.Row="0" Margin="537,454,0,0" Foreground="Red" Background="White" Opacity="0.80" Height="280" Width="500" IsHitTestVisible="False">Welcome to the Klingon Immersion Studies Holodeck program. <LineBreak />There are times when you must make a decision. <LineBreak />The D&#180;k tahg cursor will appear at those moments. <LineBreak />If the D&#180;k tahg is not visible, <LineBreak />You can pause and resume the simulation by double clicking. <LineBreak />While the program is paused, you can click some items to learn about them.<LineBreak /> <LineBreak /> ==== This game does not shy away from starting you over. Save reasonably often. ====<LineBreak /> ==== If you quit, it will not save before quitting, so Make sure you save beforehand! .====<LineBreak /> <LineBreak />  Controls:<LineBreak /> * Double Click to pause the simulation and switch to Info mode<LineBreak /> * Press + to increase volume.<LineBreak /> * Press - to decrease volume.<LineBreak /> * Press S to save.<LineBreak /> * Press Q to quit<LineBreak /> * Press &#180; for Debug Mode.</TextBlock>
                <TextBox Name="txtMS" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="537,554,0,0" Text="" TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" Grid.Row="0" Width="50"  Visibility="Collapsed"/>
                <TextBox Name="txtOffsetMs" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="610,554,0,0" Text="" TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" Grid.Row="0" Visibility="Collapsed"/>
                <ComboBox x:Name="lstScene" Grid.Row="0" Width="300" Height="20" Margin="810,52,0,0" Visibility="Collapsed" />
                <ComboBox x:Name="lstComputer" Grid.Row="0" Width="300" Height="20" Margin="810,152,0,0" Visibility="Collapsed" />
                <Canvas VerticalAlignment="Center" HorizontalAlignment="Center" x:Name="SaveDialog" Visibility="Collapsed" Width="606" Height="206" Background="DarkRed" >
